{"tid":171590,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【戀夏500日】《愛，這部分》原：旅行的意義【粵語版】","createTime":"2017-03-25T11:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T09:56:44.000Z","uid":41326,"like":29,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf9b68478d67501f0f07e0e43cdb34e5435546e","tid":171590,"uid":41326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T11:58:52.000Z","msg":"歌：<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X0-KU9DHxaQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DX0-KU9DHxaQ&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=64a48a06\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X0-KU9DHxaQ</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打絲打大家好，唔知大家有無睇過(500) Days of Summer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能套電影比較偏門<br />\n<br />\n但係小弟幾年前睇完一直覺得好深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁啱又覺得旅行的意義果種feel好切合人同人之間果種解釋唔到<br />\n<br />\n又或者無原因嘅聚散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以試下填左呢首歌<br />\n<br />\n希望大家得閒路過可以聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5107a811ea37bab2a72901b08a5ab3ddce6f00f0","tid":171590,"uid":41326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T12:00:37.000Z","msg":"主唱：KELLY YAN<br />\n填詞：挽歌之聲<br />\n<br />\n塵世許多美景追人 人像過客未懂安分<br />\n蝴蝶也拍翼飛出護蔭散播每撮花粉<br />\n<br />\n曾結識土著的村民 曾跋涉到絕嶺散心<br />\n遊歷世界萬千影像看遍了每種吸引<br />\n<br />\n亦看不穿關於愛這部分 <br />\n量度不出相戀的熱暖就算擁緊<br />\n未見加速的心跳快慢 是命脈沒養分？<br />\n還是它 尚欠半滴吻<br />\n<br />\n如客機般每天飛行 來換購紀念品轉贈<br />\n迎面每片霧霏飄近 細雨裡倍覺傷感<br />\n<br />\n沉醉千禧倒數歡騰 時代見證著入世往生<br />\n年月裡覽目經書校訓說破每句指引<br />\n<br />\n亦說不穿關於愛這部分　<br />\n描述不出相戀的甜美就算相襯<br />\n沒法假裝出一貫快樂 是浪漫沒戲分？ <br />\n還是它 尚欠缺鑲嵌<br />\n<br />\n提問愛高深 只好對鏡自問 <br />\n情話講得多深刻 情緒未有翻滾<br />\n望向窗邊星星也渴睡 是日月在抱憾 <br />\n還是它 尚欠缺共震<br />\n<br />\n未算不甘　充當過旅伴落幕亦慶幸<br />\n離席了　別探究原因<br />\n明天以後　等新舊旅客走近"},{"pid":"c7bdf04f273410274779e341e44da57b960a5b7e","tid":171590,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T12:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33661b708d9b17153b1e968a066cc2cc7abad553","tid":171590,"uid":41326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T12:02:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雪人哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585d71873c8b887c5edbfecbf48cccbb9152aa2e","tid":171590,"uid":41326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee69bd1511ea8909f30e61ee83f3dba56d85dacf","tid":171590,"uid":33507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T12:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c0a833537edf396d955a3b50ddd8fd44f544c6","tid":171590,"uid":33507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T12:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4f16ecd3e7503796e8cdac18f7e93b67c0a71d","tid":171590,"uid":33507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T13:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1c03dfed842263b3a16d371eba19b813ed3b32","tid":171590,"uid":41326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T14:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a09336d82a2f2661e124e0a572255a1a2127f09","tid":171590,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T14:42:14.000Z","msg":"嘩 好耐無見過抱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed0b812c32842d3dbb90f8d9a2cc21dc38d7fa0","tid":171590,"uid":33507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re